Package com.mare.jovan.file

Class FileMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mare.jovan.file.FileMetadata
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class FileMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    FileMetadata class is used to provide more information about certain File. It describes when file was created, how many times it was downloaded and if there is some description about file.
